outheast Australia, including the potential for less prescribed burning days and substantially greater fire danger in spring. Selecting climate models on the basis of multiple criteria can lead to more informative projections and allow an explicit exploration of uncertainty.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Clarke, Hamish", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Evans, Jason P.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Chapter 3", "biodiversity", "environment assessment", "IPBES", "Alien Invasive Species Assessment AIS", "invasive species"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/eef0f518b4b2974bcebfe7d3c7fdfb56", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/5a6c15d2f5060fcd74696e6c4a999e77be0562f66bb2648933929567425aaf99", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/2352922/items/TD6M6YS8", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/2352922/items/TD6M6YS8", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/9f3accb7c43b150c5a6e60c51e43108e!/b143950-146099", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/359bd494433933b868f85e88d3437f76", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.1007/s00704-018-2507-4", "relation": "isVariantFormOf", "resource_type": "publication", "scheme": "doi"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.7430682", "relation": "isCitedBy", "resource_type": "publication-report", "scheme": "doi"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "1", "pages": "513-527", "title": "Theoretical and Applied Climatology", "volume": "136"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/eef0f518b4b2974bcebfe7d3c7fdfb56"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.or